You are a robot with a fixed base and one gripper that can pick up and stack objects on a table.
There are two objects on the table: blue-cube-1 (a blue cube) and wooden-cube-1 (a wooden cube).
Both cubes are currently sitting on the table and nothing is on top of them.
Your gripper is empty.
Your goal is to create a stack by placing the wooden cube on top of the blue cube.
